title: Royals rally on Correa's error, beat Astros 9-6 to even ALDS
text:
> Sports Royals rally on Correa's error, beat Astros 9-6 to even ALDS Houston Astros' George Springer, right, is greeted at the plate by Colby Rasmus (28) as he scores on teammate Carlos Correa's hit against the Kansas City Royals in the fifth inning during Game 4 of baseball's American League Division Series, Monday, Oct. 12, 2015, in Houston. (AP Photo/Pat Sullivan)
